{"id":"f514c688-9631-4b73-bd02-58e64765704d","title":"1510/09/07","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"fe18f5fa-1852-4a53-98bf-26d135085513","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, September 7th, 1510.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"0d8dfdc8-f6e5-40a8-95f4-56a78545fafa","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c1ed8035-9865-4697-b892-02ae30d8cb85","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":29,"value":"07b7f667-47b3-4642-b04b-035a13782c45","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d60da6fb-8e2f-4c3a-b212-4587d518b483","type":"style/superscript","start":22,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b02e19be-71a2-44a6-8fd0-02ee5229e292","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lodovico di Buonarrota Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5a4e2d4e-f322-4bc9-b79e-3843a67834ce","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"eaedef5a-6b9b-445a-99b8-23ccb9bbee05","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"ea44dba7-6d5d-4343-aaaa-724e2090666b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"afb2e3ea-9a4c-48f7-9505-d3195130e701","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"6263300e-eeeb-4e0c-8ec5-a8b8d911470b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Dearest\u00A0Father,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0Your\u00A0last\u00A0letter\u00A0caused\u00A0me\u00A0great\u00A0disquietude\u00A0when\u00A0I\u00A0read\u00A0in\u00A0it\u00A0of\u00A0Buonarroto\u0027s\u00A0illness: wherefore, immediately on receipt of this, go to the Spedalingo and get him to give you fifty or a hundred ducats, if you have need of them, and see\u00A0that he [Buonarroto] is well provided with everything\u00A0necessary and does not go short for lack of money.\u00A0I have to tell you that I have still to receive from the Pope the five hundred ducats I have earned, and that a similar sum ought to be paid to me for putting up the scaffolding and proceeding with the other part of my work. Yet he [Julius] has gone away from here without leaving me any instructions. I have written a letter to him. I do not know what the result will be. I should have come to Florence directly I received your last letter, but if I were to go away from here without permission I fear the Pope would be greatly annoyed, and I should lose the money due\u00A0to me. Nevertheless, if Buonarroto is seriously ill, let me know at once, for if you think it advisable I will come post haste and will be with you in two days: men are worth more than money. Let me\u00A0have news quickly, because I am consumed with\u00A0anxiety. The 7th day of September.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"be6dce4f-f87a-4344-8465-ef90dd378cda","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":18,"end":21,"value":"21671569-3eea-412b-85cc-08f659f58019","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"eb898004-98d0-4f25-84ba-eac74a61610b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":28,"end":33,"value":"d7eefbaf-26ff-4da8-8f64-d49b080b9d02","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b64a8e78-1a33-4005-b08c-f76d3f008a20","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":42,"end":43,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"892c2dd3-7959-4c1a-9476-0b463a88989b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":68,"end":68,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"734c6c1f-074f-4026-bc74-baa21b1e144f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":78,"end":79,"value":"d7eefbaf-26ff-4da8-8f64-d49b080b9d02","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"dd2731ca-3cbd-43d1-9721-436a908cfb57","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":84,"end":93,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-873